dct_title_s: Santa Clara County, California GIS Maps & Data
dct_description_sm: This collection of data is produced by the County of Santa Clara County GIS program. Data layers in this collection cover a variety of themes, including: parcels. boundaries, zoning, points of interest, water supply management, public safety, and utilities. These data were downloaded from the Santa Clara County GIS Data Download site (http://gisdata.sccplanning.opendata.arcgis.com/) and the County GIS page (https://www.sccgov.org/sites/gis/GISData/Pages/Available-GIS-Data.aspx) on August 14, 2015.
System requirements: Geographic Information Systems (GIS) software that reads ESRI shapefile format.
dct_rights_sm: This item is in the public domain.  There are no restrictions on use.
